# Build context filter — keeps the builder image small and rebuilds fast.
# Anything NOT needed at compile time lives here.

# Git + tooling
.git/
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github/

# IDE / editor
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Local config / state
.env
.envrc
.DS_Store
*.log

# CI metadata
.codegraph/
.claude/

# Build output
config-extractor
go-daemon-config-extraction
env-printer

# Generated CA bundle (re-created inside the builder at build time)
internal/infrastructure/tls/certs/ca-certificates.crt

# Old repo-root cert stash (no longer used)
certs/

# Tests stay — `go test ./...` is not run inside the image, but the test
# files are tiny and harmless. Remove the next line if you want a strict
# production-only context.
**/*_test.go